com.vmware.esx.settings.depots

Class AffectedDesiredStateInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.esx.settings.depots.AffectedDesiredStateInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StaticStructure, Structure, java.io.Serializable

    public final class AffectedDesiredStateInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, StaticStructure
    The AffectedDesiredStateInfo class contains the fields that describe which release units in the desired state will be affected by the depot to be deleted or disabled. This class was added in vSphere API 7.0.3.0.
    See Also:
